name: Special Broadcasting Service (SBS)
title: Who Do You Think You Are S16 Ep4
content: **Who Do You Think You Are? Australia: Season 16 Episode 4Gina Chick** Author and adventurer Gina Chick sets out to find the identity of her biological grandfather and the source of her wild ways. Her investigation leads her to a story of extraordinary courage and resilience in the face of tragedy.
